text.section:
The notice of intent to prospect shall be in writing and submitted on forms prescribed by the Department. The notice shall include:
A description of the area to be prospected;
A description of the legal basis upon which the person who intends to prospect claims the right to enter and conduct prospecting operations on the area;
A description of the intended prospecting operations;
A statement of the period of the proposed prospecting; and
A plan for reclamation of the area in accordance with the requirements of this subtitle upon completion of the prospecting.
